# xcodeMetrics.ProductData

**Object**

The metrics information of an app on a specific platform.

## Declaration

```swift
object xcodeMetrics.ProductData
```

## Objects

- **xcodeMetrics.ProductData.MetricCategories**: A metric category and its associated array of data and measurements.

## Objects

- **xcodeMetrics.Insights**: Analysis of power and performance data collected for your app that includes regressions and trends.
